define dragon as the list frame take nat_to_whole xii layer 
    layer 
        cycle entirely by xxiv shift east swinging_tail 
        cycle entirely shift_by pos xxi pos vii center_head 
    cycle entirely shift_by pos xxvii pos iv layer
        right_half 
        for vi rotate entirely 
            shift west 
            entirely flip_over_y right_half

