define right_half as the list frame layer
    layer
        entirely shift_by pos vi pos vii layer
            cycle cat blow roar
            cycle for 
                iii 
                rotate_right 
                entirely shift_by pos xv zero fire
        cycle entirely 
            shift_by pos x pos i 
            append new_frame wing
    layer 
        cycle slow ii entirely shift_by pos iv neg i foot
        cycle for ii rotate for ii extend art x vii
